ED_Title: Observer status for the International Parliamentarians’  Congress in the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: At its 47th plenary meeting, on 4 December 2024, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Sixth Committee, (A/79/488, para.7.)  decided to defer a decision on the request for observer status for the International Parliamentarians’ Congress in the General Assembly (Footnote: See A/78/141.)  until the eightieth session of the Assembly.
